reviews.text: Love the airry and bright atmosphere of the restaurant with a hip vibe. The afternoon tea is a treat and not too expensive by HK hotel standards. The service is very good and so is the food. They seem to run themed high teas in conjunction with a partner so on this occasion there was a pineapple theme for the sweet pastries. The scones were fabulous, freahly made and moist. They had a twist on the traditional raisin scone, serving chocolate and orange instead which was a nice twist. Would definitely recommend and visit again.

Went for Happy Hour, cocktails are great! And had afternoon tea there a couple of times. Food is lovely and service is great! 

Very cozy place with natural light:) 

Food 4/5
Drink 4/5
Service 4/5
Ambience 4/5

Tried the impossible burger and it's surprisingly well ! 
Nice texture patty with  bit if charcoal grill flavor
Food is good and tasty.  The impossible burger is worth a try.
going into Green and relax, one of my best afternoon tea spot over the years.

reviews.text: 開心的下午茶，一早book定位，要預先繳交二百蚊落訂。因是慶祝結婚周年紀念，book枱時留了呢個message，想不到會有一碟小點做驚喜。食物水準真的一般，甜點比咸點出色得多。服務員十分有禮貌，女的很細心為我們移枱，怕被隔離小朋友們嘈到。環境十分舒適，餐廳樓底很高，有自然光透射落黎，舒暢。是日甜點以台灣微熱山丘作主題，很多點心都加有菠蘿作買點～～

GREEN Spring Sensations Afternoon Tea Set ($546/2, plus 10% service charge) 🌸 Hotel ICON新推出的春日果漾下午茶，有無限供應的HÄAGEN-DAZ雪糕雪條，簡直是女孩子的福音❤️個人認為咸品都好有驚喜，咸點有🍴紅桑子鵝肝、🐟蘇格蘭煙三文魚多士、🍄蘑菇芝士批、🥒芝麻帶子、🍅鮮茄沙律撻。而甜品有罌粟子檸檬蛋糕、朱古力咖啡貝殼蛋糕、柑橘青檸乳酪蛋糕、法式紅桑子蛋糕和軟心朱古力。一路食，一路影相，輕輕鬆鬆。👭
餐廳環境幾舒適，今次來食下午茶餐，主題是微熱山丘的鳳梨酥，其他大部份食物都有用鳳梨做，算是切合主題，也好吃的，但整體不算十分特出，又覺當中有些食物過甜了。

環境唔錯，安静。前菜和小菜都有水準，芒果同蟹肉很合，蟹餠有點散不過係好食，而蟹腳燒得很香，多汁爽口。但主菜會參差，我地本身叫3成熟，出嚟就一邊生熟不均，有點失準，牛肉淋身都幾香。甜品不過不失。
侍應唔夠主動，比如加酒之類。
整體都唔錯，味道可以。

Green在酒店大堂位置， 樓底好高沒有壓迫感， 空間充斥著似曾相識嘅 JoMalone  Lime Basil & Mandarin 氣味。
星期三 晚餐ladies night cocktail任飲， 當中一杯士多啤梨味嘅cocktail最好飲。
 頭盤係海鮮拼盤食完其實都已經擺咗一大半， 加埋個主菜已經好飽，甜品我哋選咗但都，真係好好味 。
想搵一個地方同朋友傾足全晚、 有急凍海鮮、有甜品有酒飲、輕鬆一下 ，價錢服務費係四百幾蚊。推介！

reviews.text:
Well Done on their wine pairing with the truffle eggs and truffle shrimps. Wine pricing is 10-15% less than normal hotel. Friendly service, recommend to try. 

6pm - 8pm daily is normally for their club guests and not serving walk-in (I recommend they should consider 5pm - 7pm instead ☺️)

Great hotel very polite and helpful staff. Hotel is very environmentally aware as limousine and buses are electric, all bathroom items are plastic free. Level of service is great, mini bar is free and access is provided, via a phone, to mobile internet and it allows you to call home free. Food is excellent.  Really enjoyed my stay

Hotel Icon was amazing! Jessica made our stay even more special by greeting us with champagne and providing helpful tips for our stay. It was also so great to have a nice gym in the hotel that offered all of the equipment needed. I'd love to come back!

Located in heart of Hong Kong, Hotel Icon offered nice view to the harbour which is awesome. Easy access to everywhere. The services is great, all staff welcoming nicely and so helpfully.  They also have tea time which is super cute and delicious. The food was great, however on the Gala Dinner, the chicken bit rare.

Beautiful and modern.  Great room view of the harbor and amenities.   Free mini bar which is restocked every day.   Also, a Handy cell phone that is free to borrow.  You can use it to tour the city, and make local and international phone calls!!! 🙂
